1) Total order revenue - Calculated column (as it needs to be calculated in real-time when you save the order);
2) Inv on hand - Whole number Column?? What if we have inventory units of measure as not only whole numbers? Like weight, volume, etc. Rollup wouldn't work as it is async and recalculated on a schedule. Key and Autonumber are eliminated by definition. So, probably, the whole number is the correct option.
3) SharePoint as they ask to share a folder
